   BIBLE PALETTE (only these colors allowed):
   - pageBg: #F4F1EB (宣纸白)
   - cardBg: #FAF8F4 (古纸色)
   - gold:   #C8A24A (淡金)
   - goldLight: #E8D8B4 (鎏金)
